Maximal Efficacy. MBio. 2016 Aug 9;7(4)</p></body></sub-article></sub-article><sub-article id="REPORT27005" article-type="peer-review"><front-stub><article-id pub-id-type="doi">10.21956/aasopenres.14053.r27005</article-id><title-group><article-title>Reviewer response for version 1</article-title></title-group><contrib-group><contrib contrib-type="author"><name><surname>Meiring</surname><given-names>James E.</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="A10">1</xref><xref ref-type="aff" rid="A11">2</xref><role>Referee</role><contrib-id contrib-id-type="orcid">https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9183-5174</contrib-id></contrib><aff id="A10">
